We are looking forward to returning to Lynchburg this Sunday, December 17th at 2:30pm for the youth skills clinic!

EasyMan (Jeand Doest) put on an amazing Nutmeg Entertainment Show at Halftime! Shoutout to @mandocorrales for connecting us and we are excited to return to Lynchburg today from 2:30-5:00pm for a youth clinic and Adult Futsal action with Armando! See you soon!

🐺 Another successful ShadowTek Futbol Youth Clinic, Nutmeg Entertainment Show and Adult Futsal all with special guest @easymantv 🙌

We wanted to give a big shoutout to Armando Corrales, Dizo and their entire crew at Passage for making these events such a huge success!

🙌 We also wanted to thank the nonprofit organization, Passage, for supporting our Lynchburg events by helping with recruitment, graphic design, marketing & logistics. Passage works with over 100 players each week through it’s 3 main outreaches: Elite, Old Goats and Lynchburg Soccer.

Also a big thank you to Timberlake Christian School for providing the facility for our Wednesday event and to Liberty Christian Academy (LCA) for our Sunday event! Thank you to @cvusoccerclub for your support of our clinics as well! We had so much fun at your “United We Give” charity event!
